This is what 39 looks like. I made it this far. Never looked like I had #cancer and all my health issues and problems. As I reflect I can proudly say I have no idea what I am doing. All I know is I have a #passion and a #drive and it keeps me going and I will always get back up and keep going. I know who and what I am and what I am here to do. That is all we can hope to figure our. My #wife asked me if I had any epiphanies and no but what I can say is I learned in recent years we have no control of anything and life happens to you so you just have to figure out how to flip your perspective and keep a positive attitude. #actor #rapper #comedian #impressionist #voartist #DJ #mc #host #paranormalinvestigator #Parapsychology #paranornaldetectives #talenteded #birthday #crystalcove

Today is one year exactly from when I had my surgery to remove the cancerous tumor on my left kidney. I was  a medical anomaly with zero symptoms of all the problems it caused me. A month before I found this out I lost almost my whole family to covid. My wife stayed by my side and so many people in my life showed me love and support. Thanks to UCLA and Dr. Chamie I am alive to inspire people to go after their dreams like I am. I have kept my promise to never work a normal job again and continue to get new opportunities for all my talents. #cancer #survivor #fcancer #beatcancer #alive #inspire #actor #rapper #talent #talenteded #comedian #impressionist #parapsychologist #paranormalinvestigator #talenteded #mcpierre #keepgoing #nevergiveup #life
